jparsec.time.calendar

Class MayanHaab

  • java.lang.Object
    • jparsec.time.calendar.MayanHaab
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MayanHaab
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Implements the Mayan Haab calendar. See Calendrical Calculations for reference.

    Note that it is not possible to pass from a given date to a Julian day, since no year exists in this calendar.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    T. Alonso Albi - OAN (Spain)
    See Also:
